title: All for love, or, The happy match betwixt Jockey and Jenny Jockey and Jenny have struck up a bargain, and Jockey took Jenny without e're a farthing, Jenny had nothing, and Jockey enough, but Jockey he lov'd her, and this is the proof. Tune of, Sawny and Jockey.
publisher: Printed for P[hilip]. Brooksby in West-smithfield,
